关于```WebHook```推送，可以使用```Golang```编写的服务程序：

```
package main
import (
    "fmt"
    "net/http"
)            

func Handle (w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {
    defer func() {
        fmt.Println("req:", *r)
    }()
}            

func main () {
    fmt.Println("listen http://localhost:9090")
    http.HandleFunc("/data", Handle)
    http.ListenAndServe(":9090", nil)
}
```

在[推送设置](https://www.fmz.com/m/account)中设置```WebHook```：```http://XXX.XX.XXX.XX:9090/data?data=Hello_FMZ```，
运行写好的```Golang```服务程序后，开始实盘运行策略，以下为```JavaScript```语言编写的策略，策略运行时执行```Log()```函数并推送消息：

```js
function main() {
    Log("msg", "@")
}
```

```Golang```语言编写的服务程序接收到推送，服务程序打印信息：

```
listen http://localhost:9090
req: {GET /data?data=Hello_FMZ HTTP/1.1 1 1 map[User-Agent:[Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10_9_3) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/xx.x.xxxx.xxx Safari/537.36] Accept-Encoding:[gzip]] {} <nil> 0 [] false 1XX.XX.X.XX:9090 map[] map[] <nil> map[] XXX.XX.XXX.XX:4xxx2 /data?data=Hello_FMZ <nil> <nil> <nil> 0xc420056300
```

